You are asked to design a game-based money transfer application.

Here is how it works:
1. When User perform the first trannsaction of sending actual curreny to a sender - both sender and reeiver gets 100 Virtual SuperCoins.
2. In all the successive transactions, only the sender receives some Gifts randomly.
3. These Gifts are virtual Super Weapons:
-- Balloon [10 SuperCoins]
-- Water Gun [20 SuperCoins]
-- Candy Bombs [30 SuperCoins]
4. User can uses their Weapons to attack other users, and  capture that many corrosponding SuperCoins from the other users SuperCoin balance. 
5. After collecting certain number of SuperCoins, you can one-way transfer them to actual currency, say 1,00,000 = $1.

Advanced:
Address race conditions.